    "sections": {
        "description": "<p>This tiny plugin adds silently the viewport meta tag with zooming permission to give your users the ability to zoom in your website with mobile browsers.<\/p>\n<p>If you find yourself in trouble not to be allowed to zoom with your favourite smartphone in your theme,<\/p>\n<p>You can take this tiny plugin just to get the shiny magic zooming with your smartphone in your theme.<\/p>\n<p>There are themes which are &#8220;responsive&#8221;. But a few of them are cruel. They do not let you zoom in-to your theme.<\/p>\n<p>Don&#8217;t be upset, don&#8217;t get in panic, don&#8217;t spend a lot of money. Allow mobile zooming definitely in your theme.<\/p>\n<p>You just download this plugin and click to activate it. No options page, no settings. Just your theme.<\/p>\n<p>This plugin does all the magic for you and your users zooming with your smartphone in your theme.<\/p>\n<p>Instead, just adding a second viewport meta line in the header section of a page, I started with version 1.5.0 to add theme specific viewport replacement, if available.<br \/>\nIf you know theme which allows changes in the viewport by a filter, please write a comment in the <a href=\"https:\/\/wordpress.org\/support\/plugin\/definitely-allow-mobile-zooming\" rel=\"ugc\">WordPress forum<\/a> and I will add the specific filter.<\/p>\n<p>If you find yourself in trouble with this tiny plugin, don&#8217;t hesitate to ask for <a href=\"https:\/\/wordpress.org\/support\/plugin\/definitely-allow-mobile-zooming\" rel=\"ugc\">support<\/a>.<\/p>\n<p>Try it out on your free dummy site and <a href=\"https:\/\/demo.tastewp.com\/definitely-allow-mobile-zooming\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">click here<\/a>.<\/p>\n<p>The plugin does not collect any personal data, so it is ready for EU General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) compliance. In your theme.<\/p>\n",
        "installation": "<p>&#8220;Definitely allow mobile zooming&#8221; needs only activation to take effect. Pick one of the following ways to make the plugin work.<\/p>\n<h4>Using The WordPress Dashboard<\/h4>\n<ol>\n<li>Navigate to the &#8216;Add New&#8217; in the plugins dashboard<\/li>\n<li>Search for &#8216;Definitely allow mobile zooming&#8217; or just &#8216;allow zooming&#8217;<\/li>\n<li>Click &#8216;Install Now&#8217;<\/li>\n<li>Activate the plugin on the Plugin dashboard<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<h4>Uploading in WordPress Dashboard<\/h4>\n<ol>\n<li>Navigate to the &#8216;Add New&#8217; in the plugins dashboard<\/li>\n<li>Navigate to the &#8216;Upload&#8217; area<\/li>\n<li>Select <code>definitely-allow-mobile-zooming.zip<\/code> from your computer<\/li>\n<li>Click &#8216;Install Now&#8217;<\/li>\n<li>Activate the plugin in the Plugin dashboard<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<h4>Using FTP<\/h4>\n<ol>\n<li>Download <code>definitely-allow-mobile-zooming.zip<\/code><\/li>\n<li>Extract the <code>definitely-allow-mobile-zooming<\/code> directory to your computer<\/li>\n<li>Upload the <code>definitely-allow-mobile-zooming<\/code> directory to the <code>\/wp-content\/plugins\/<\/code> directory<\/li>\n<li>Activate the plugin in the Plugin dashboard<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n",
        "changelog": "<h4>1.6.0<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>added better viewport compatibility for Flatsome theme (thanks to @bramvds)<\/li>\n<li>Tested successfully up to WordPress 6.3<\/li>\n<li>Tested successfully up to WordPress 6.4<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.5.0<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>added better viewport replacement for OceanWP theme<\/li>\n<li>Tested successfully with WordPress 5.8<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.4.1<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Tested successfully with WordPress 5.6.2<\/li>\n<li>Tested successfully with WordPress 5.7<\/li>\n<li>new branding<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.4<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Tested successfully with WordPress 5.5.1<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.3<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Tested successfully with WordPress 5.2.1<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.2<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added &#8216;Requires PHP&#8217; info in readme.txt<\/li>\n<li>Tested successfully with WordPress 4.9.1<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.1<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Successfully tested with WordPress 4.8<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.0.7<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Successfully tested with WordPress 4.7<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.0.6<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Successfully tested with WordPress 4.6<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.0.5<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Successfully tested with WordPress 4.5<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.0.4<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Successfully tested with WordPress 4.4<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.0.3<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Successfully tested with WordPress 4.3<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.0.2<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Successfully tested with WordPress 4.1<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.0.1<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Successfully tested with WordPress 4.0<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.0<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>First release. I hope it works with your website.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n",
        "reviews": "<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Perfect!<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/esp2013\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/61bf65a54c1d67860455f03aff4286b6?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/61bf65a54c1d67860455f03aff4286b6?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/esp2013\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">esp2013<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">March 1, 2024<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">This did the trick and saved me from writing a function - thanks!<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Won&#039;t Work on Pop Ups<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"4 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"4\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/jazzylane11\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/74e6fcf78ad765cd23913be7f4cd0a0c?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/74e6fcf78ad765cd23913be7f4cd0a0c?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/jazzylane11\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">jazzylane11<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">October 7, 2023<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">Cheers, very handy - HOWEVER I can't get it to work on Pop Ups (Popups for Divi) on a mobile device. Any tricks you'd be able to share? Thanks heaps. <\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Saved my bacon - THANKS!<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/greymouse\/\"><img alt='' src